{
  "comment": "Shared agent-docs canonical-status corpus. Each case describes an on-disk layout, the effective policy, and the expected verdict+flags per instruction directory ('' = project root). Asserted by BOTH tests/test_agent_docs_canonical.py (Python classifier) and app/src-tauri agent_docs.rs #[test] (Rust scanner) so the two implementations can never diverge.",
